item.title: Try to add construction base
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:
@pure2ownage wrote:

The event system that the tutorial used is not within your server, use this tutorial to add it, then all you need to do is rename it a little (or modify your own code, to make it work with it). Then make sure you import it in all classes that use it. Otherwise you can write your own or find an alternative system.
